Invocation Name: book eater
des:
Book Eater will search aggregate sites to locate the web/light novel that you are looking for and tell you the latest release. You don't have to refresh a page or keep a tab open anymore. Simply ask Book Eater to check for you.

Currently supported search engines: NovelUpdates (NU)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
